      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Hearing that these spaces feel like band-aids on a gaping wound makes complete sense, and the desire to stop the struggle entirely is a rational response to such chronic pain. Your feelings of hopelessness are valid, especially when facing a world that often feels wired to be against you. However, while the exhaustion is real, choosing to walk away entirely can sometimes remove the only path to genuine freedom or escape available to you.",
